Lock Some Equipment

From the menu, tap Enhancements.
On the Enhancements screen, tap View/Sell to see the gear you currently possess.
Touch and hold the gear you'd like to lock to open a details window.
Then tap Lock to lock that gear.
Locked gear cannot be sold or used as an enhancement material.
You can also lock gear after obtaining it from a draw.
5★ weapons are valuable pieces of gear, so it's a good idea to lock it whenever you get one.
